name: Meanwell LRS-350-24V AC/DC Power Supply
metaTitle: Meanwell LRS-350-24V AC/DC Power Supply | Onco Solutions
metaDescription: Discover the Meanwell LRS-350-24V, a compact, high-efficiency 350W power supply ideal for LED lighting and industrial control systems. Features 89% efficiency and full protection.
shortDescription: The MEANWELL LRS-350 series is a compact, high-efficiency switching power supply designed for industrial applications. With 89% typical efficiency, full protection features, and a 1U low-profile design, it's ideal for LED lighting, industrial control systems, and telecommunications equipment.
description_points: Ultra-compact 1U low-profile design for space-constrained installations
Built-in over-voltage, over-load, and short-circuit protection
Cooling by free air convection (no fan required)
